{"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of buttons","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"button"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSButton","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllButtonComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"ButtonComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"buttons","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Button","type":"text"}]},{"text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"), borders","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for button component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the button component tokens you want.","","        override var buttonSizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens.dimension600 }","","        override var buttonBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.borderWidthThicker }","","        override var buttonBorderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.borderRadiusMedium }","","        override var buttonColorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.colorRepositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","","        override var buttonSpacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.spacePaddingInlineSpacious }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider: ButtonComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Then, you can give this ","type":"text"},{"code":"CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to your own theme implementation:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(button: CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    OrangeTheme(button: CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let buttonComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, borders, colors and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let buttonComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider","                                                spaces: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.9.0","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Since"}]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/AllButtonComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent06ButtonB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8Copyable